{"tid":317842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大學生宿舍女生墮樓　送院不治","createTime":"2017-07-11T17:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T00:09:12.000Z","uid":52574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a331aa72ed197892ea812c94b46bd14330b78c24","tid":317842,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170712/mobile/bkn-20170712000756951-0712_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170712%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170712000756951-0712_00822_001.html&d=8BBDh6HsE5LcO4ODcw7cS49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8bb8fbb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170712/mobile/bkn-20170712000756951-0712_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍塘歌和老街香港城市大學學生宿舍，昨晚11時許，一名20餘歲女子於上址高處墮下，當場重傷昏迷，其後由救護車急送明愛醫院搶救後證實不治。死者身上無身份證明文件，據悉為該校學生，警員正在跟進墮樓原因。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"fde5bc97999096f2db45647a79ec7bfbf511f38e","tid":317842,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"岸狗舞若衣"},{"pid":"53b790a3fe7262bcce51e318ea7a80333d13a508","tid":317842,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35096c4404ec75945421c3b1728617444b7b3f92","tid":317842,"uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"又有人喺hall跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw rip"},{"pid":"6ab5c98066f80cb39b2d6d42926898799a4093d3","tid":317842,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"052373fc3c1c786a8e2ce78718929cc227d152a0","tid":317842,"uid":20724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/012559_2a1fadc2e